# Laravel Package Creator

## When to use

- Creating a new Laravel package from scratch
- Setting up Service Provider, Facade, config, routes, and migrations
- Configuring package testing with Pest/PHPUnit and Orchestra Testbench
- Publishing a package to Packagist with proper composer.json

## Keywords

`laravel package`, `ServiceProvider`, `Facade`, `composer.json`, `testbench`, `vendor:publish`, `package:discover`, `main branch`, `PackageServiceProvider`
